metadata.name: MYSTERIOUS FOREST #1
metadata.description: Be careful when you go to the forest. The paths are winding and can lead very far, sometimes itâ€™s even scary to imagine how far. The swamp is very deep and beckoning to dive into them and drown.  The branches of the trees grab the shoulders and wrap around the neck.  Heavy clouds crush you with their greatness, threatening to flatten you like an ant. You catch yourself thinking that it would be better to run around the clearing and pick flowers under the blue sky, but the forest beckons.
